  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Astro Boy centers around a boy-robot named Astro that tries to bridge the relationship between humans and robots. This game is based on the computer-animated superhero film named \"Astro Boy\".\nThis Nintendo DS version offers a different artstyle and more classic 2D platforming experience compared to the PSP, PS2 and Wii versions that utilize more 3D-looking graphics while keeping the platforming to a more 2,5D experience",
